          <div class="h-1 w-16 sm:w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow-xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 md:gap-10 items-center">
              <div class="flex justify-center order-2 md:order-1">
                <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Portfolio image"
                    class="w-48 sm:w-56 md:w-64 h-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-700" />
              </div>
              <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6">
                  Who Am I?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3 sm:mb-4">
                  I am a final-year student aspiring to become a skilled Backend and Frontend web developer. I have hands-on experience developing web apps using Laravel and MySQL, and also desktop apps with VB.net. I've explored data analysis with R Studio and Python.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Currently, I'm diving into Astro.js and learning advanced backend technologies and cloud computing. I also love reading tech blogs and working on personal projects.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- Skills Section with Animated Cards -->
